descriptionHtml:
In this mod, the dwarvens are getting alive, what means there are dwarvens replaced in Blackreach 
It adds ~ 20 new Characters, 5 new rooms, 2 seller and a treasury camber with traps. Also there is in the trasury camber a new item, called big gold ingot, which you can smelt and get 50 gold ingots  . There\'s a magic , too. To come to blackreach u need a key, which is at your home in Markarth ;
with it you can open the secret door behind in your home and the door in the trasury house.
